Package: sftpr
Title: Wrappers to work with SFTP connections
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Sam", "De Meyer", , "sam.demeyer93@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides a set of functions to work with SFTP servers. It allows uploading and downloading files, and wrapping other R functions to work seamlessly with SFTP URLs.
